-- Trump Entertainment Resorts Names Robert Griffin as CEO, Replacing Juliano
-- B y   J o A n n e   N o r t o n
-- 2010-09-28T18:03:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-28/trump-entertainment-resorts-names-robert-griffin-as-ceo-replacing-juliano.html
Trump Entertainment Resorts
Inc. said it appointed Robert F. Griffin as chief executive
officer and board member.  Griffin has been president and CEO of MTR Gaming
Group Inc. He replaced Mark Juliano, who will leave the company,
Trump Entertainment said.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
JoAnne Norton at 
 jnorton@bloomberg.net  